The paper deals with deep learning models for character recognition tasks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) domains. Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it deals with character recognition.
